%TMPL:DEF{"heading"}%Topic is locked by another user%TMPL:END%
%TMPL:DEF{"message"}%
There is a possibility that <b> %PARAM1% </b> is editing this topic. <br />
Please ask the contributor before making changes to this topic.
<ul>
  <li> To look at the text without editing the topic click on the [[%SCRIPTURLPATH%/view%SCRIPTSUFFIX%/%WEB%/%TOPIC%?raw=on][View raw text]].</li>
  <li> To edit anyway click on the <a href="%SCRIPTURLPATH%/edit%SCRIPTSUFFIX%/%WEB%/%TOPIC%?t=%SERVERTIME{"$year$mo$day$min$sec"}%&breaklock=on">Edit anyway</a>. 
     Note, that this will _break_ the lock&nbsp;%I%</li>
  <li> To cancel simply go <a href="javascript:history.back()">back</a> in your browser.</li>
</ul>
<form class="natOopsButtons" name="ButtonBox">
  <input style="color:red" type="button" value="Edit anyway" onclick="window.location.href='%SCRIPTURLPATH%/edit%SCRIPTSUFFIX%/%WEB%/%TOPIC%?t=%SERVERTIME{"$year$mo$day$min$sec"}%&breaklock=on'">&nbsp;
  <input style="color:blue" type="button" value="View raw" onclick="window.location.href='%SCRIPTURLPATH%/view%SCRIPTSUFFIX%/%WEB%/%TOPIC%?raw=on';">&nbsp;
  <input style="color:green" type="button" value="Cancel" onclick="history.back()">
</form> 
%I% __Note:__ Locking gets reset after <b> %PARAM2% </b> minutes of inactivity, 
the earliest in <b>%PARAM3%</b> minutes. 
%TMPL:END%
